about your sister.

18:41.620 --> 18:42.890
I don't have any.

18:42.950 --> 18:44.390
Let's go look at her.

18:44.450 --> 18:45.920
Maybe that will help.

18:45.990 --> 18:48.590
Oh, she looks sad.

18:48.660 --> 18:50.660
That's 'cause she knows
you're looking at her.

18:50.730 --> 18:52.330
Although I'm aware you're
looking at me,

18:52.390 --> 18:55.960
I would look exactly the same
even if you weren't.

18:56.030 --> 18:58.940
( <i>piano playing soft jazzy pop)</i>

18:59.000 --> 19:00.970
<i>Bart, think.</i>

19:01.040 --> 19:02.940
<i>What happens to you</i>

19:03.000 --> 19:04.670
when you turn eight?

19:04.740 --> 19:07.710
Well, your training wheels
come off your bike.

19:07.780 --> 19:09.180
Good. That's good.

